rows.label: qst003104_msg0001
rows.name:
Are you here to help with
the distribution, Sir?

rows.label: qst003104_msg0003
rows.name:
This distribution center is short
on dishes made with fish, Sir.

rows.label: qst003104_msg0004
rows.name:
If you could prepare some
fish dishes, I would like
you to bring them here, Sir.

rows.label: qst003104_msg0005
rows.name:
Your cooperation is
greatly appreciated, Sir!

rows.label: qst003104_msg0006
rows.name:
Some say it's gotten busier since the
Acedian refugees arrived, but...

rows.label: qst003104_msg0007
rows.name:
I am a new recruit, Sir! I
am doing all I can just to
handle my own duties, Sir!

rows.label: qst003104_msg0008
rows.name:
Honestly, I have not had
the luxury of worrying
about the refugees, Sir!

rows.label: qst003104_msg0009
rows.name:
But thanks to all of you, I have
a little more leeway now, Sir!

rows.label: qst003104_msg0010
rows.name:
From now on, I intend to
pay much more attention to
all those in need, Sir!

rows.label: qst003104_msg0011
rows.name:
Thank you very much!
I am grateful, Sir!
